<time_sig>8.8.6.D.</time_sig>
<title>Pin Chihowa Chitokaka ƲIT7</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Pin Chihowa Chitokaka,
 Ʋba in Chihowa yoka
.    
     E holitoblashke.
 Yʋmmak osh pi̱ Mi̱ko yoke;
 Im okla talaia pia,
 Iloh i̱ yimmashke

[V2]
 Chihowa ilʋppak ocha
 hupi Okchalinchi yoke;
.    
     Iloh ahninchashke:
 Ilʋppak fehna bano hosh
 Hʋpin Chihowa mak oke
.    
     Il anukchetashke

[V3]
 Chihowa okcha̱ya a̱hli
 Bilia ilʋppak okʋt
.    
     Ʋba Pi̱ki yoke;
 Yohmi ka̱ hʋpishno ʋto
 Im ʋlla hʋpia hoke;
 Iloh i̱ hullashke.

[V4]
 Chisʋs im issish pulla ka
 Isht pi ai ʋlhchefa kʋto,
.    
     Nitak kanima ho̱,
 Yakni nana a palʋmmi,
 Issʋt iʋt ʋba onʋt,
 E foha hi oke.

[V5]
 Chisʋs i̱ yimmi biekʋt
 Ahninchit e maha̱yakma,
.    
     Ʋba Pi̱ki yokʋt
 Ant pi hoyokma, ʋba ya̱
 Iʋt, ont il aiasha na
 Bilia hi oke.</lyrics>
<aka>The Christian's God and Saviour.</aka>
</song>